### HYMN XVI

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501601">1</span></span>His first
downward breath is the time of Full Moon.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501602">2</span></span>His second
downward breath is the eighth day after Full Moon.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501603">3</span></span>His third
downward breath is the night of New Moon.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501604">4</span></span>His fourth
downward breath is Faith.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501605">5</span></span>His fifth
downward breath is Consecration.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501606">6</span></span>His sixth
downward breath is Sacrifice.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1501607">7</span></span>His seventh
downward breath are these sacrificial fees.

